  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education Support for 150 Deaf Children,Bangalore</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The school is facing challenge to provide quality education on regular basis due to shortage of funds for meeting salaries of special teachers, other staff, safety measures, hearing aids, and school maintenance.  Government and other donors are supporting to cover 80% of the total costs needed for providing quality education to 150 deaf children.   Therefore, it still leaves a critical gap of 20% costs. This shortfall would put the education of 150 disabled children at stake.</narrative>
  </description>
